QuestData.Title: An Offering for Soo-rahm
QuestData.Description: We not know you, stranger, but we know you want something.$B$BWe will talk to Bones of Nozronn for you, but you must bring us offerings. We need powerful emperor cobra fangs to complete our oracle's necklace.$B$BGo to the Wildgrowth Mangal, northeast of our hut, find cobras and bring back best fangs. Then we make bones speak to you.
QuestData.LogDescription: Bring 5 Intact Cobra Fangs to Oracle Soo-rahm, near the Bones of Nozronn.
QuestData.CompletionText: We must know -- do you bring fangs?
QuestData.RewardText: <The oracle inspects the fangs.>$B$BWe approve! Bones of Nozronn will speak to $n!
